  "texts": [
    "It provides SMEs with a centralized view of their security posture, aggregating and correlating data from multiple sources and enables them to respond quickly to security incidents and mitigate potential damages.",
    "This paper presents a technical analysis and evaluation of some of the most popular opensource SIEM solutions that are suitable for SMEs, namely, Wazuh, AlienVault OSSIM, SIE-Monster and Elastic Security.",
    "In this work, we performed a detailed evaluation and comparison of the security and performance features of these SIEM solutions.",
    "For performance evaluation, we deployed each SIEM solution in a testbed that is representative of a typical enterprise network of an SME.",
    "EPS evaluation was done by generating logs from various network devices and collecting and processing them by the SIEM system."
